trans-unit.source: Represents a property of a printing system hardware or software component whose value is an array of <xref href="System.Byte"></xref> values.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintByteArrayProperty"></xref> class for the specified attribute.
The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Byte> array property of a print system object, including casing.
The name of the property, which is an array of type <xref href="System.Byte"></xref>, that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintByteArrayProperty"></xref> represents.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintByteArrayProperty"></xref> class that has the specified value for the specified attribute.
The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Byte> array property of a print system object, including casing.
The name of the property, which is an array of type <xref href="System.Byte"></xref>, that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintByteArrayProperty"></xref> represents.
The value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintByteArrayProperty"></xref> represents.
Gets or sets the value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintByteArrayProperty"></xref> represents.
A boxed array of <xref href="System.Byte"></xref> values.
